    "Id": "chassisdef_texihuitl_TEX-R6",
    "Name": "Texihuitl",
    "Details": "The R6 uses only a 300 Light engine, but in turn can fit two Heavy MRM-60 and one Heavy MRM-45 launcher, together with 6 tons of ammunition. A single ER Large Laser is even mounted to provide some extra firepower once the munitions run dry. The cooling is still the major weakness of the design, as prolonged battles was never the goal of the RISC engineers when creating the Texihuitl.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - HMRM</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.43</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
